    "# SECTION A — Cleaning (Opportunity-level)\n",
    "\n",
    "This section creates a canonical opportunity-level dataset that is typed, de-duplicated, and safe to use downstream.  \n",
    "The goal is a single consistent source of truth before panel construction and modeling."
   ]
